simulation.agent.variant

Interface VariantAgent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Agent, Listener, Speaker
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TotalListener, TotalSpeaker

    public interface VariantAgent
extends Agent
    An interface for defining variant agents for computer models of language evolution. Such agents can interact with other agents in accordance with specifically defined rules.
    See Also:
    TotalSpeaker, TotalListener
